Title: Analyze configuration: Avoid crash on timeout when contacting remote sites
Level: 1
Component: wato
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.5.0p25
Date: 1588168378
Class: fix

In case of connection problems of remote sites, the analyze config page crashes
with a RequestTimeout. From now on, a warning message is displayed for failed
sites and the page is rendered correctly.
